19:53.610 --> 19:54.987
Well, you have to try.

19:55.070 --> 19:58.866
Well, I have tried,
but she's not a likable person.

20:01.326 --> 20:04.329
She's been a lifeline to me.
She really has.

20:04.413 --> 20:05.998
- She's a wonderful person.
- Mm.

20:06.081 --> 20:08.333
Well, you're mistaken.

20:08.417 --> 20:11.753
Did I ever tell you
that she once saved Max from drowning?

20:11.837 --> 20:13.130
- Really?
